<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:59:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国盛和将收购匹克稀土坦桑尼亚项目一半股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-shenghe-acquire-half-peak-rare-earths-tanzania-project-2024-07-24/</link><description>澳大利亚 Peak Rare Earths 周三表示，中国矿商盛和资源公司将收购一家英国公司 50% 的股份，该公司拥有其坦桑尼亚 Ngualla 项目 84% 的股权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-shenghe-acquire-half-peak-rare-earths-tanzania-project-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，英伟达批准三星 HBM3 芯片用于中国市场处理器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，三星电子的第四代高带宽内存或 HBM3 芯片已首次获得 Nvidia 批准用于其处理器。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>新日铁将解散与中国宝钢成立20年的合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/nippon-steel-dissolve-jv-with-chinas-baoshan-after-20-years-2024-07-23/</link><description>新日铁周二表示，将解散与中国宝山钢铁的合资企业，现有股东协议将于八月底到期，从而结束二十年的合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 22:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/nippon-steel-dissolve-jv-with-chinas-baoshan-after-20-years-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>波音恢复向中国交付737 MAX飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resumes-deliveries-737-max-airplanes-china-2024-07-23/</link><description>波音公司周二表示，在因监管问题导致长时间延迟后，该公司已恢复向中国交付最畅销的 737 MAX 飞机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 21:54:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resumes-deliveries-737-max-airplanes-china-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>随着芯片需求稳定，TI 季度利润超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-ti-beats-second-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-07-23/</link><description>得益于个人电子产品等市场对模拟芯片的需求稳定以及制造成本的降低，德州仪器 (TI) 周二第二季度利润超出了分析师的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-ti-beats-second-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能订单抵消了中国销售额下降后，ASMI 上调了季度指引</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</link><description>计算机芯片制造设备供应商 ASM 国际公司 (ASMI) 周二表示，由于人工智能相关产品抵消了中国销售额的下降，第二季度订单超出预期，该公司上调了第三季度指引。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>渔业条约在世贸组织失败引发中美担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</link><description>周二，削减渔业补贴的条约草案未能通过后，各国和环保组织表达了担忧和失望，中国呼吁各国对世界贸易组织的谈判方式进行重大改变。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，苹果最早可能会在 2026 年发布可折叠 iPhone</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</link><description>据周二报道，苹果公司可能最早在 2026 年推出可折叠 iPhone，这可能标志着该公司最受欢迎产品的最大硬件设计改造。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场放缓，路威酩轩集团销售额未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</link><description>尽管西方市场的需求略有回升，但由于中国消费者控制了国内高端时装的支出，路威酩轩第二季度的销售增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰外长抵达中国讨论“公平和平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</link><description>乌克兰外长周二抵达中国，与外交部长王毅举行会谈，讨论如何在与俄罗斯的战争中实现“公平和平”，并讨论双边关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在兴奋剂纠纷中向美国挑战金牌炫耀权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国来到巴黎奥运会，期待着近几十年来亚洲体育强国屡见不鲜的金牌潮，但兴奋剂纠纷的阴影却笼罩着代表团。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在中国举步维艰。电动汽车能否帮助其在美国发展？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</link><description>当大众集团上个月向美国电动卡车和 SUV 制造商 Rivian 投资 50 亿美元时，这家初创公司的股价因现金注入而飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:59:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</guid></item><item><title>中国鼓励部分企业利用外债提振实体经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-encourages-some-firms-tap-foreign-debt-boost-real-economy-2024-07-23/</link><description>根据网上发布的官方声明，中国最高经济规划师周二表示，将支持优质企业借用中长期外债，支持实体经济发展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-encourages-some-firms-tap-foreign-debt-boost-real-economy-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表达担忧后，克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯与中国的北极合作不针对任何人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯与中国在北极的合作并不针对任何其他国家，并表示美国对此类工作的批评是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国大型基金经理设定薪酬上限，收回超额工资以推动“共同繁荣”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/big-chinese-fund-managers-cap-pay-claw-back-excess-common-prosperity-push-2024-07-23/</link><description>五位直接了解此事的人士表示，中国两家领先的基金管理公司已经限制了员工的年收入，并将收回超出的部分，这是政府紧缩政策下针对该行业的首次此类措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:27:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/big-chinese-fund-managers-cap-pay-claw-back-excess-common-prosperity-push-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>